title: Suspicious Azure Run-Command
id: 6745e010-bca4-49a2-9ec2-92a1e7957744
status: experimental
description: Detects suspicious AZ VM run-command invoke from a windows host.  This should be executed infrequently and unexpected executions should be investigated.  
references:
    -   https://support.scythe.io/knowledge/azure-resource-group-backdoor    
author: Tyler Casey @1qazCasey, @scythe_io
date: 2024/03/28
tags:
    - attack.execution
    - attack.1059
logsource:
    product: windows
    category: proc_creation
detection:
    selection:
        CommandLine|contains:
            - 'az vm run-command invoke'
    condition: selection
falsepositives:
    - Administrators may use this for Azure VM management.
level: 
    - medium